<template>
    <section>
        <el-table
                :data="data"
                style="width: 100%">
            <el-table-column
                    prop="date"
                    label="Date"
                    width="180">
            </el-table-column>
            <el-table-column
                    prop="name"
                    label="Name"
                    width="180">
            </el-table-column>
            <el-table-column
                    prop="address"
                    label="Address">
            </el-table-column>
        </el-table>
    </section>
</template>

<script>
    import {mapState} from "vuex";

    export default {
        name: "Debts",
        computed: {
            ...mapState("persons", {
                data: s => s[this.$route.name.toLowerCase()],
            }),
        },
        mounted() {
            this.$store.dispatch('persons/GET_TABLE', {table:'debts'})
        }
    }
</script>

</style>
